{"tid":499129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上侮辱南京大屠殺死難者　河北男被捕行政拘留15日","createTime":"2017-12-14T12:54:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T03:52:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bc60e9dfff103b54ba200f48a463d41ddfbcd7b4","tid":499129,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T12:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171214/s00001/52ab5b6cb6bf96e08516d1d3368bd138.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F52ab5b6cb6bf96e08516d1d3368bd138.jpg&h=8e47b70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河北滄州任丘市一名網民，星期三在網上發言侮辱南京大屠殺死難者：「南京大屠殺還是死的中國人少！不然我怎麼還是娶不上媳婦呢？大日本天皇萬歲！」言論引起廣大民眾不滿，當地公安部門隨後表示接到舉報，傳召一名姓王男子至公安機關，判罰15日行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n任丘公安表示，王男涉嫌違反《中華人民共和國治安管理處罰法》，已承認在網上發表不當言論。警方表示，網絡不是法外之地，網民需牢固樹立法治觀念和自律意識，建設一個健康、有序、和諧的網絡空間。<br />\n<br />\n（新浪微博、任丘公安）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513255793384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513255793384&d=6QxlN6fDmcXkHnYsSNDSXJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=cfe0ebfb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171214%2Fs00001%2F1513255793384&h=59ac8c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171214/s00001/1513255793384</a>"},{"pid":"0c21194f972a5587b864d4b5d7c8fecaae690984","tid":499129,"uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f309fd9256b79cea5bd646f9c0e2e9d1ab4011a0","tid":499129,"uid":139766,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T13:16:06.000Z","msg":"趁23條仲未實行 連登仔儘早及時行樂吧<br />\n唔係就無機㗎啦 不正當言論charge鳩u"},{"pid":"678596fd15ac2efe0d8bed13b7d34